gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Magic 127, Spurs 111
gameRecap.excerpt: The Magic defeated the Spurs, 127-111. Franz Wagner led the way for the Magic with 34 points, seven rebounds and seven assists, while Paolo Banchero added 16 points, five rebounds and six assists in the victory. Devin Vassell tallied 30 points, five rebounds and four assists for the Spurs in the losing effort. The Magic improve to 28-24 on the season, while the Spurs fall to 10-42.
